<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3927918>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Ophiothrix spiniformis n. sp.: A, Dorsal view of the disc; B, SEM of the disc spine; C, detail of radial shields covered by short spines; D, oral frame; E, dorsal arm plates; F, ventral arm plates; G, SEM image of dorsal arm plate; H, SEM image of ventral arm plate (ZUEC 02374, holotype, Paraná, Brazil). Scale bars: A, C–F = 1 mm; B = 500 μm; G–H = 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3927918/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3927920>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. SEM photographs of vertebrae and arm spines of Ophiothrix spiniformis n. sp.: A, proximal surface; B, distal surface; C, dorsal surface; D, ventral surface; E, lateral arm plate; F, arm spine (ZUEC 02374, holotype, Paraná, Brazil). Scale bars: A–D = 200 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3927920/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

